ary any no hihinananareo sy ny ankohonanareo eo anatrehan' i Jehovah Andriamanitrareo ary hifalianareo amin' izay rehetra harin' ny tananareo , izay efa nitahian' i Jehovah Andriamanitrao anao . ||| Both you and your families must feast there before the Lord your God and rejoice in all the output of your labor with which he has blessed you .
