dia eo amin' ny tany izay hofidin' i Jehovah Andriamanitrareo hampitoerany ny anarany no hitondranareo izay rehetra andidiako anareo , dia ny fanatitra doranareo sy ny fanatitrareo hafa alatsa @-@ drà sy ny fahafolon @-@ karenareo sy ny fanatitra asandratry ny tananareo , ary izay zavatra tsara ataonareo voady amin' i Jehovah . ||| Then you must come to the place the Lord your God chooses for his name to reside , bringing everything I am commanding you - your burnt offerings , sacrifices , tithes , the personal offerings you have prepared , and all your choice votive offerings which you devote to him .
