fa eo amin' ny tany izay hofidin' i Jehovah ihany amin' ny firenenao anankiray no hanateranao azy , sady eo koa no hanaovanao izay rehetra andidiako anao . ||| for you may do so only in the place the Lord chooses in one of your tribal areas - there you may do everything I am commanding you . Regulations for Profane Slaughter
