eny , aza mihinana azy ianao , mba hahita soa ianao sy ny taranakao mandimby anao , raha manao izay mahitsy eo imason' i Jehovah ianao . ||| You must not eat it so that it may go well with you and your children after you ; you will be doing what is right in the Lord 's sight .
